	Recent Developments





	Trading Update




	Our total sales
	(including exports) of Tata Motors vehicles in January and February 2015 were 42,582 vehicles and 44,209 vehicles respectively, representing increases of 5% and 11% over the sales in January and February 2014. However, on a cumulative basis, as of
	February 28, 2015, we had sold only 449,659 vehicles for the fiscal year ended March 31, 2015, as compared to 515,407 vehicles in the equivalent period in the fiscal year ended March 31, 2014, representing a decline of 13%.


