	Fractional ADS Rights



	Fractional ADS Rights will not be issued. Fractional entitlements to ADS Rights will be rounded down to the nearest whole number and will lapse without compensation.




	 





	Unexercised ADS Rights



	ADS Rights that are not exercised prior to the end of the ADS Rights Offering subscription period will expire valueless without any compensation.




	 





