	respect of such investors subscription in the applicable ASBA account. The SCSB would then transfer the payment from the applicable ASBA account to a designated account of our company pursuant to instructions from the Registrar. Securities
	subscribed for pursuant to the ASBA process can only be allotted in dematerialized form.


	 




















