	OUR PRINCIPAL RISKS



	Risks are identified, assessed and measured
	against a defined set of criteria to consider the likelihood of occurrence and potential impact to the business facilitated by our Enterprise Risk Management framework. Plotting our principal risks on a risk map helps to visualise each risk profile
	as well as targeting to bring each risk back within a tolerable level.



