	The capital structure is governed according to Company policies approved by the Board and is monitored by various metrics such as debt to Adjusted EBITDA and
	Adjusted EBITDA to interest ratios, as per the debt covenants and rating agency guidance. Funding requirements are reviewed periodically with any debt issuances and capital distributions approved by the Board.



